INSERT INTO `dr_server_conferenceinfo` VALUES ('1297', 'International Conference on Metallurgy Technology and Materials', 'ICMTM', ' ', 'Xi an, China', '2020-04-25', '2020-05-13', '2020-05-13', '8', '2020 8th International Conference on Metallurgy Technology and Materials (ICMTM2020)\r\nSession Description\r\n2020 8th International Conference on Metallurgy Technology and Materials (ICMTM2020) will take place from 1-2, August, 2020 in Xi\'an, China.\r\nThe conference focuses primarily on Metallurgy, Mining Engineering, Advanced Materials Science and Materials Processing Technology. The conference and the publications arising from it will trigger further related research and technological improvements in this important field. This conference provides opportunities for the delegates to exchange new ideas and application experiences, to establish business or research relations and to find global partners for future collaboration.\r\n	Conference Venue: Xi\'an, China                \r\n	Conference Date: August 1-2,2020\r\n	Conference web: http://www.icmtm.org\r\nThe paper publication\r\nAll accepted and registered papers will be published in conference proceeding in the international journal “Solid State Phenomena\"【ISSN: 1662-9779 】. And the press will submit all papers to major databases such as EI Compendex, Scopus and Scholar...\r\nConference Theme\r\nThe main topics of interest include but will not be limited to the following.\r\nT1: Metallurgy Materials \r\nT2: Metallic glass \r\nT3: Metal alloy Materials \r\nT4: Materials Forming \r\nT5: Advanced Materials Science \r\nT6: Materials Processing Technology\r\nFor more topics details, you can click http://www.icmtm.org/cfp.html \r\nImportant Dates\r\nSubmission Deadline:June 30, 2020 \r\nConference Date: August 1-2, 2020 \r\nPaper Submission\r\nEmail:  cfp@icmtm.org\r\nCMT: https://cmt3.research.microsoft.com/ICMTM2020\r\nContact Us \r\nEmail ：cfp@icmtm.org\r\nWebsite: http://www.icmtm.org\r\nTel: +86-24-83958379', 