INSERT INTO `dr_server_conferenceinfo` VALUES ('1684', 'International Conference on Graphics, Images and Interactive Techniques', 'CGIIT', ' ', 'Beihai, China', '2021-02-25', '2020-08-20', '2020-09-20', '5', '5th International Conference on Graphics, Images and Interactive Techniques (CGIIT 2021) will be held in Beihai, China during Feb. 25-28, 2021. The ultimate aim is to promote different ideas to offer a place for participants to present and discuss their innovative recent and ongoing research and theoretical work and/or their applications or development. The organizing committee of conference is pleased to invite prospective authors to submit their original manuscripts to CGIIT 2021. The topics of CGIIT 2021 cover Graphics, Images and Interactive Techniques, etc. Topics of interest for submission include, but are not limited to\r\n \r\nComputer Graphics\r\nModeling\r\nRendering\r\nHCI/user interfaces\r\nGraphical models\r\nModel Validation\r\nComputer Art\r\n3-D object Extraction\r\nAI techniques\r\nComputer Aided Design\r\n\r\nImage and Graphics\r\nAdvanced image processin\r\nComputational cameras\r\nComputational illumination\r\nComputational optics\r\nHigh-performance imaging\r\nMultiple images and camera arrays\r\nSensor and illumination hardware\r\nScientific imaging and videography\r\nOrganizing and exploiting photo/video collections\r\nVision for graphics\r\nGraphics for visio\r\n\r\nVisualizations\r\nVisualization, Virtual Reality and Augmented Reality\r\nMedia immersion\r\nGraphics User Interface\r\nInformation Visualization\r\nVisualization Software\r\nComputer Games\r\nGraph and Network Visualization\r\nReal-Time Simulation\r\nHuman Perception\r\nOther related topics\r\n\r\nInteractive Techniques\r\nSocial networks interaction\r\nCrowd computing\r\nUser interfaces for multitudes\r\nMassive interaction platforms\r\nMassive Open On-line Courses or MOOCs\r\nOn-line cooperative work\r\nCrowdsourcing\r\nCitizen Science\r\nModels for Crowd-Computers Interac